  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are about 15m² have a traditional décor. They can sleep up to two people and have side lake views, air conditioning, TV, free Wi-Fi, tea &amp; coffee making facilities (on request), minibar, safe, hairdryer and bathtub or shower. Rooms with a balcony and lake view are available for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> sleep up to three people. They're made up of a standard side lake view room and a single room, with a shared bathroom. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Terrace Rooms</strong> sleep up to two people and have lake views. The terrace has deckchairs and a table. They have a bath with a showerhead attachment. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Double Rooms for Single Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
